headline: Ignore The Valuation And Buy The Growth In Intuitive Surgical (ISRG)
summary: Intuitive Surgical (ISRG) is set to roll out its Da Vinci 5 robot in 2025. This positions the company well for significant growth in the coming years. However, investors remain concerned about the company’s high valuation. We believe this concern isn’t justified, as the company’s position as a market leader justifies the high premium associated […]
